OL,3,CYorkshire Water to pay out #40m after
OL,4,Csewage overflow failings
OL,6,FYorkshire Water has been forced to pay
OL,7,Fout #40 million to address failings
OL,8,Fover wastewater and sewage.
OL,10,FIndustry watchdog Ofwat said a probe
OL,11,Finto the company found "serious
OL,12,Ffailures" over how it operated and
OL,13,Fmaintained its sewage network,
OL,14,Fresulting in excessive spills from
OL,15,Fstorm overflows.
OL,17,FThe regulator said Yorkshire Water had
OL,18,Fadmitted responsibility and agreed to
OL,19,Fthe enforcement package.
