OL,3,CYorkshire Water to pay out #40m after
OL,4,Csewage overflow failings
OL,6,FIt will pay out #36.6 million over the
OL,7,Fnext five years to prioritise work on
OL,8,Fparticularly problematic storm
OL,9,Foverflows in environmentally-sensitive
OL,10,Fareas.
OL,12,FThe water firm, which supplies more
OL,13,Fthan five million customers, will also
OL,14,Fhand #3.4 million of funding to the
OL,15,FGreat Yorkshire Rivers Partnership.
OL,17,FIt comes as Yorkshire Water is set to
OL,18,Fhike its annual bill for customers by
OL,19,F29% from 1 April.
