OL,3,CYorkshire Water to pay out #40m after
OL,4,Csewage overflow failings
OL,6,FLynn Parker, senior director for
OL,7,Fenforcement at Ofwat, said: "Our
OL,8,Finvestigation has found serious
OL,9,Ffailures in how Yorkshire Water has
OL,10,Foperated and maintained its sewage
OL,11,Fworks and networks, which has resulted
OL,12,Fin excessive spills from storm
OL,13,Foverflows.
OL,15,F"This is a significant breach and is
OL,16,Funacceptable.
