OL,4,Csewage overflow failings
OL,6,F"We are pleased that Yorkshire Water
OL,7,Fhas recognised this failure and is
OL,8,Ftaking steps to put it right for the
OL,9,Fbenefit of customers and the
OL,10,Fenvironment.
OL,12,F"We now expect them to move at pace to
OL,13,Fcorrect the remaining issues our
OL,14,Finvestigation has identified."
OL,16,FNicola Shaw, chief executive of
OL,17,FYorkshire Water, said: "We know our
OL,18,Fstorm overflows operate more
OL,19,Ffrequently than we, or our customers,
OL,20,Fwould like them to.
